To celebrate its 12th anniversary in the Kingdom, LuLu Hypermarket has announced a host of shopping deals and prizes to be won from Nov. 7-20. The LuLu Super Fest will select 1,000 surprise winners across its 20 stores in Saudi Arabia to award gift vouchers worth SR1,000 each — a total of SR1 million. Since the winner is selected through the hypermarket’s point of sale system at check-out, the rewards are instantaneous. Moreover, the anniversary promotion comes packed with super deals — featuring 50 best products across all categories, in-store promotions, “Berry Fest,” live demonstrations, hourly offers, auction sales and exchange offers. Shoppers can update their electronic devices to the latest ones with affordable prices on branded laptops, tablets, smart watches, mobile phones, high-end audio devices, printing consumables and accessories. Brands participating in the promotion will also give away freebies and special gifts. “The success of LuLu Hypermarket is our bond with our Saudi Arabian customer base — their trust and their recognition of our quality promise has enabled our growth,” said Shehim Mohammed, director of LuLu Hypermarkets Saudi Arabia. “This never-before offer combines our commitment of customer care, quality and affordability and is our thank you to all our customers in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia,” he added.